title: TWIZTID  W.I.C.K.E.D
description:
W.I.C.K.E.D. will be released in three different versions. Best Buy will sell an exclusive version with 3 additional tracks. Hot Topic will sell a version with a comic based on the song "Bella Morte" included, and a third version sold at various music stores will include an enhanced disk including music videos for the songs "Buckets of Blood" and "Ha Ha Ha Ha Ha Ha". Psychopathic Records' store Hatchetgear will be selling all three versions, in addition to a standard version without any extras. All versions from Hatchetgear will come with one Psychopathic Records Trading Card.Album was leaked on March 11, 2009
